14/12/2008
NICOSIA, Cyprus -- The Council of Ministers announced on Saturday (December 13th) a three-day period of mourning for former President Tassos Papadopoulos. 
He died of lung cancer Friday at the age of 74. 
The funeral will take place on Monday, when all public institutions will be closed. 
(CNA, Xinhua - 13/12/08)
